stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> onCreate: 用户触发启动
    onCreate --> onStart
    onStart --> onResume
    onResume --> onPause: 失去焦点
    onPause --> onStop: 完全不可见
    onPause --> onResume: 重新获得焦点<br/>(如 Dialog 关闭)
    onStop --> onRestart: 用户返回
    onRestart --> onStart
    onStop --> onDestroy: finish() / 系统回收
    onDestroy --> [*]
    onCreate --> onDestroy: 极端情况<br/>(onCreate 中 finish)

    state "onCreate()" as onCreate
    state "onStart()" as onStart
    state "onResume()" as onResume
    state "onPause()" as onPause
    state "onStop()" as onStop
    state "onRestart()" as onRestart
    state "onDestroy()" as onDestroy

    note right of onResume: 前台 - 可见可交互
    note right of onPause: 部分可见 - 不可交互
    note right of onStop: 不可见 - 后台
